            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"startLocation\": \"Delhi Warehouse\",\n  \"destinationLocation\": \"Noida Hub\",\n  \"startTime\": \"2026-05-10T09:00:00\",\n  \"endTime\": \"2026-05-10T11:00:00\",\n  \"direction\": \"OUTBOUND\",\n  \"points\": [\n    {\n      \"locationName\": \"Delhi Warehouse\",\n      \"latitude\": 28.6315,\n      \"longitude\": 77.2167\n    },\n    {\n      \"locationName\": \"Noida Hub\",\n      \"latitude\": 28.5708,\n      \"longitude\": 77.3261\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "description": "Private API. Creates a route for a vehicle.\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST '{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/riders/vehicle/{{vehicleId}}/routes' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -H 'X-Client-Id: {{clientId}}' -H 'X-Client-Password: {{clientPassword}}' -d '{\"startLocation\":\"Delhi Warehouse\",\"destinationLocation\":\"Noida Hub\",\"startTime\":\"2026-05-10T09:00:00\",\"endTime\":\"2026-05-10T11:00:00\",\"direction\":\"OUTBOUND\",\"points\":[{\"locationName\":\"Delhi Warehouse\",\"latitude\":28.6315,\"longitude\":77.2167},{\"locationName\":\"Noida Hub\",\"latitude\":28.5708,\"longitude\":77.3261}]}'\n```",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/riders/vehicle/{{vehicleId}}/routes"
          }
        },
