            "description": "Creates a shipment. Shipment type examples: `LONG_HAUL`, `INTER_HUB`, `LAST_MILE`.\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST '{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/warehouse/shipments' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{\"shipmentType\":\"LONG_HAUL\",\"originWarehouseId\":\"{{warehouseId}}\",\"destinationWarehouseId\":\"{{destinationWarehouseId}}\",\"parcelIds\":[\"{{parcelId}}\"],\"vehicleId\":\"{{vehicleId}}\",\"departureTimeEst\":\"2026-05-10T10:00:00+05:30\",\"arrivalTimeEst\":\"2026-05-10T14:00:00+05:30\"}'\n```",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/warehouse/shipments"
          }
        },
